{"tid":1039531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預算案後另公布「補漏拾遺」措施？　陳茂波：目前不覺有需要","createTime":"2019-02-27T12:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T13:03:20.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c2992a3d73dde33254b1bc9b25eb5c61fe9942","tid":1039531,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"財政司長陳茂波今早發表《財政預算案》，對於今年繼續有聲音認為，部分市民未能從預算案中受惠，陳茂波晚上在預算案論壇中表示，今年有500多億元財政盈餘，已有400多億是經由退稅、退差餉及長者醫療券增加1000元等一次過的措施回饋市民，「比例不算少」。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波認為，今年預算案已屬「比較平衡」的方案，故目前政府不覺得有需要如去年般，在《財政預算案》公布後再另外提出「補漏拾遺」措施。<br />\n<br />\n去年《財政預算案》公布後，外界提出有市民未能受惠，政府「聽了大家意見，自己亦檢討思考後」決定推出關愛共享計劃，讓合資格市民可申領4000元或扣減相關稅務及差餉寬減後的差額。"},{"pid":"886c203e9b38c8091e9920b7ccc147cda145471f","tid":1039531,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190227/s00001/1551270338474/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551270338474%2F&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c3c1b656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551270338474%2F&h=b228e145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190227/s00001/1551270338474/</a>"},{"pid":"00e1ad44c4bda7bcce239d834250e7545cc4118d","tid":1039531,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"今年佢叻呀<br />\n老綜 生果金 都少過舊年<br />\n咁咪唔洗補漏~ 因為大家都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71415df76a64bc027c63ae78e90f359584c6cb96","tid":1039531,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99be7916390d6afdfb680f2790dd6c44c1a2d86","tid":1039531,"uid":22566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"呢招好呀 <br />\n一年閪過一年 唔嘈就質質膊 一嘈就隊拾遺補漏<br />\n慳慳埋埋又一舊錢拎來圈<br />\n<br />\n世界級政府"}]}